<div class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 recap bottom">
  <h1 class="text-center"><%= @round.course %></h1>
  <h4 class="text-center comment_handle"><%= @round.user.name %> | <%= @round.created_at.strftime("%m-%d-%Y") %></h4>
    <br /><br /><br />

  <div class="show-stats">
    <div class="col-xs-4 text-center big-score show-stats">
        <h4 class="comment_handle">Score</h4>
        <%= @round.score %>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-4 text-center big-score show-stats">
        <h4 class="comment_handle">Greens Hit</h4>
        <%= @round.greens %> / 18
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-4 text-center big-score show-stats">
        <h4 class="comment_handle">Driving Accuracy</h4>
        <%= @round.fwys %> / <%= @round.fwystotal %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="show-stats">
      <div class="col-xs-4 text-center big-score bottom">
        <h4 class="comment_handle">Putts</h4>
      <%= @round.putts %>
      </div>

      <div class="col-xs-4 text-center big-score bottom">
        <h4 class="comment_handle">Birdies</h4>
        <%= @round.birdies %>
      </div>

      <div class="col-xs-4 text-center big-score bottom">
        <h4 class="comment_handle">Pars</h4>
        <%= @round.pars %>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
<br class="clr" />
<div class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 round-recap top bottom">
  <div class="container">
    <h3>Let's look at your round from another perspective....</h3>
    <br />
    <p class="info">
      <% if @round.birdies > 0 %>
      <% total_stretch_under = @round.birdies + @round.pars %>
      You had <%= @round.birdies %> birdies and <%= @round.pars %> pars. If you think about it, you played <%= total_stretch_under %> holes at <%= @round.birdies %> under!
      <% else %>
      <% total_stretch = @round.pars %>
      You had <%= @round.birdies %> birdies and <%= @round.pars %> pars. If you think about it, you played <%= total_stretch %> holes at EVEN par!
      <% end %>
    </p>
    <p class="info">
      <% total_holes_left = (18 - (@round.pars + @round.birdies)) %>
      What happend on the last <%= total_holes_left %> holes?
      How was your chipping? How many times did you get up and down for par
      on the remaining <%= total_holes_left %> holes?<br />
      Did you have poor tee shots or did you have a bad
      approach to the green? Was your chip close or did you chip to 10' or 15' and miss the putt?
      Think about the holes where you could have improved and it should help you to focus on areas that need
      attention to help you lower your score!
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
